    "c-spacing": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Spacing\n\n**Base unit** 4px\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `xs` | 4px |\n| `sm` | 8px |\n| `md` | 16px |\n| `lg` | 24px |\n| `xl` | 40px |\n| `2xl` | 64px |\n| `3xl` | 96px |\n\nAll spacing values are integer multiples of the 4px base unit.",
