    },
    "c-type": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Typography\n\n| Step | Size | Weight |\n|---|---|---|\n| h1 | 3.5rem | 300 |\n| h2 | 2.5rem | 300 |\n| h3 | 1.75rem | 400 |\n| h4 | 1.25rem | 400 |\n| body-1 | 1rem | 400 |\n| body-2 | 0.875rem | 400 |\n| label | 0.75rem | 500 |\n\nLabel tracking: +0.08em. All line heights: 1.4–1.6.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
