    "c-motion": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Motion\n\n**Durations**\n\n- `fast` 150ms\n- `base` 300ms\n- `slow` 500ms\n- `xslow` 800ms\n\n**Easing**\n\n- `ease-out` exits\n- `spring` interactions\n- `linear` progress bars\n\n**Stagger** 60ms per item. Entrance delay cap: 400ms.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
